---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Consolidate Hutang 2026',
  slug: 'consolidate-hutang-2026',
  excerpt: 'Gabungkan semua hutang dalam satu. 0% deposit. Kurangkan interest, mudah urus.',
  date: '2026-01-19',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Refinancing',
  image: '/images/blog/consolidate-debt-2026.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['consolidate hutang', 'debt consolidation malaysia', '0% deposit', 'gabung loan'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/${lang}/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Refinancing</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
          <span>{post.author}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{post.readTime} min baca</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Banyak Hutang? Susah Urus?</h2>

        <p>Punya 5-10 loan lain-lain? Different due date? Different interest? Consolidate semua dalam satu. Mudah urus, kurangkan stress.</p>

        <h2>Contoh Debt Consolidation</h2>

        <p><strong>Sebelum Consolidate:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Loan 1 (Excavator): RM3,500/bulan</li>
          <li>Loan 2 (Lori): RM2,000/bulan</li>
          <li>Loan 3 (Forklift): RM800/bulan</li>
          <li>Loan 4 (Personal): RM1,000/bulan</li>
          <li>Loan 5 (Credit Card): RM500/bulan</li>
          <li><strong>Total: RM7,800/bulan</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Sesudah Consolidate:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Single loan: RM4,000-5,000/bulan</li>
          <li><strong>Jimat: RM2,800-3,800/bulan!</strong></li>
          <li>Satu due date je</li>
          <li>Lower rate</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Bank vs Kami</h2>

        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: #D4A574;">
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Item</th>
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Bank</th>
              <th style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #D4A574; text-align: left;">Kami</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Collateral</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Perlu property</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Equipment OK</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background: #F9FAFB;">
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Kelulusan</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">3-4 minggu</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>24-48 jam</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Process</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">Complicated</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;"><strong>Simple</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2>Kelebihan Debt Consolidation</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>Satu payment je</li>
          <li>Lower overall interest</li>
          <li>Easier to manage</li>
          <li>Less stress</li>
          <li>Better cash flow</li>
          <li>Fokus pada satu lender je</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Nak Consolidate Hutang?</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Kami gabungkan semua loan anda dalam satu. 0% processing fee. WhatsApp kami.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
        <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan Sekarang" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
      </footer>
    </article>
  </BaseLayout>

  <style>
    h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
    strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
    ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
    li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
    li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
